      <textblock>
        Patients with Crohn's disease from 4 tertiary referral centers.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Newly diagnosed of Crohn's disease within 6 months

          -  Must record their symptom in a web-based symptom diary at least 4 consecutive times
